8
00:00:28,117 --> 00:00:29,830
  ~ Revenge Note 1 ~

9
00:00:31,291 --> 00:00:34,043
  Episode 6

10
00:00:36,957 --> 00:00:38,418
My gosh.

11
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:41,801
Who is it?

12
00:00:50,349 --> 00:00:52,663
Deok Hui.

13
00:00:52,663 --> 00:00:54,975
What is it? What's wrong?

14
00:00:54,975 --> 00:00:56,705
What happened?

15
00:01:03,023 --> 00:01:06,465
So you ran away from home?

16
00:01:07,487 --> 00:01:10,269
I'm never going back home.

17
00:01:10,269 --> 00:01:12,983
Deok Hui, can I stay here for a few days?

18
00:01:12,983 --> 00:01:15,354
That's fine,

19
00:01:15,354 --> 00:01:18,336
but why did you run away from home?

20
00:01:27,177 --> 00:01:28,547
  My goodness.

21
00:01:28,547 --> 00:01:30,640
  Why do you have to eat so fast?

22
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,972
  Let your oppa have some. Can't you see how thin he is?

23
00:01:32,972 --> 00:01:34,704
  You're really...

24
00:01:34,704 --> 00:01:36,795
  Here, eat up.

25
00:01:37,807 --> 00:01:40,559
  Aigoo, look how well you eat.

26
00:01:40,559 --> 00:01:43,963
  My baby even eats like an angel.

27
00:01:45,445 --> 00:01:47,778
  You do know that my only joy in life is

28
00:01:47,778 --> 00:01:50,730
  seeing your face every day, right?

29
00:01:53,242 --> 00:01:55,645
  What's wrong with her? How rude.

30
00:01:55,645 --> 00:01:58,138
  Gu Hui, get back here or there will be no food for you.

31
00:01:58,138 --> 00:02:01,069
  - I'm not eating!  
 - That little...

32
00:02:02,581 --> 00:02:06,286
  What on earth has gotten into her all of a sudden?

33
00:02:06,286 --> 00:02:10,520
  They say adolescents are a handful. She's just really making me grow old.

34
00:02:17,728 --> 00:02:19,590
  Are you hungry?

35
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:22,120
  That's why you should've eaten when you could.

36
00:02:27,026 --> 00:02:28,739
  I'm going to make some *bibimmyeon.  
 (*cold mixed noodles)

37
00:02:28,739 --> 00:02:31,241
  - Do you want some? 
 - No.

38
00:02:31,241 --> 00:02:33,312
  - I'm full. 
 - Are you sure?

39
00:02:33,312 --> 00:02:34,914
   I'll make just one portion then.

40
00:02:34,914 --> 00:02:39,027
  - You better not try to take any later. 
 - Enjoy it all you want.

41
00:02:53,592 --> 00:02:56,605
  That looks really good.

42
00:02:59,139 --> 00:03:01,060
  Gu Hui, can I have a bite?

43
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:03,693
  No, I already asked you before if you wanted some.

44
00:03:03,693 --> 00:03:05,395
  Can I have just one bite?

45
00:03:05,395 --> 00:03:07,027
  - I said no. 
 - I swear,

46
00:03:07,027 --> 00:03:08,947
  I'll really only have one bite.

47
00:03:13,243 --> 00:03:15,134
  - I'm watching you. 
 - Okay.

48
00:03:16,286 --> 00:03:19,038
  No, that's not a bite. Take less.

49
00:03:19,038 --> 00:03:20,879
  - Like this? 
 - Gosh.

50
00:03:22,502 --> 00:03:26,756
  - This is only a few strands of noodles. 
 - Yes.

51
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,572
  You...

52
00:03:32,572 --> 00:03:35,926
  You said you didn't want any!

53
00:03:35,926 --> 00:03:38,058
  You're eating it all!

54
00:03:38,058 --> 00:03:41,561
  My goodness. Can't you share with your brother?

55
00:03:41,561 --> 00:03:44,715
  Why is someone small like you so greedy over food?

56
00:03:44,715 --> 00:03:46,605
  Gu Jun, do you want me to make you another one?

57
00:03:46,605 --> 00:03:50,380
  No, that was a really filling bite.

58
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:54,034
  It was mine. I made it for myself!

59
00:03:54,034 --> 00:03:56,115
  Why did you eat the whole thing?

60
00:03:56,115 --> 00:03:59,449
 Aigoo... That's nothing to scream about.

61
00:03:59,449 --> 00:04:02,420
  Fine. I'll make you another one!

62
00:04:04,874 --> 00:04:06,636
  Oh, my.

63
00:04:07,958 --> 00:04:10,118
  I can't believe that girl.

64
00:04:12,963 --> 00:04:15,095
  It's not because of the bibimmyeon.

65
00:04:15,095 --> 00:04:17,627
  Why do I always get treated this way?

66
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:24,364
So you ran away from home over a bowl of bibimmyeon?

67
00:04:24,364 --> 00:04:25,875
No.

68
00:04:25,875 --> 00:04:30,489
I'm not saying it's over the bibimmyeon. It's not about the food.

69
00:04:31,610 --> 00:04:35,264
The one getting on my nerves isn't my mom.

70
00:04:35,264 --> 00:04:37,366
It's my brother.

71
00:04:37,366 --> 00:04:40,080
Why? Oppa Gu Jun

72
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:43,083
is tall, handsome and sweet.

73
00:04:43,083 --> 00:04:44,454
I wish I had an oppa like him.

74
00:04:44,454 --> 00:04:47,337
He only acts normal outside of the house.

75
00:04:47,337 --> 00:04:50,741
He's a completely different person at home.

76
00:04:50,741 --> 00:04:52,342
  Hey, Gu Hui,

77
00:04:53,552 --> 00:04:54,995
  take this.

78
00:04:54,995 --> 00:04:57,356
  What's this?

79
00:04:57,356 --> 00:04:58,958
  This is expensive.

80
00:04:58,958 --> 00:05:01,190
  What's the occasion? Is this really for me?

81
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:02,853
  Yes, eat up.

82
00:05:02,853 --> 00:05:05,444
  I love you, Gu Jun.

83
00:05:05,444 --> 00:05:08,809
  But eat it and stay in your room.

84
00:05:08,809 --> 00:05:10,630
  Why?

85
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:12,482
  My friends are coming over later,

86
00:05:12,482 --> 00:05:15,343
  and it's embarrassing because you're ugly.

87
00:05:18,118 --> 00:05:19,890
That's hilarious.

88
00:05:19,890 --> 00:05:23,131
Your brother really knows how to lay down the facts.

89
00:05:25,495 --> 00:05:29,688
  I can't believe this. How could my baby get disqualified?

90
00:05:29,688 --> 00:05:31,682
My oppa must've gotten disqualified.

91
00:05:31,682 --> 00:05:33,242
You have an oppa?

92
00:05:33,242 --> 00:05:36,386
My mom recently adopted an oppa.

93
00:05:36,386 --> 00:05:38,828
- He's even younger than I am. 
 - But your mom is a fan of Eun Woo.

94
00:05:38,828 --> 00:05:40,950
You know how easily my mom falls in love.

95
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,793
How could this happen?

96
00:05:42,793 --> 00:05:47,306
Samuel is young, handsome and talented.

97
00:05:47,306 --> 00:05:50,400
I'll make him debut myself.

98
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:53,032
I'll break my savings account for you!

99
00:05:53,032 --> 00:05:54,805
Wait for me, Samuel!

100
00:05:54,805 --> 00:05:57,777
It's making me so angry.

101
00:05:57,777 --> 00:06:00,699
Why did he have to get disqualified?

102
00:06:02,701 --> 00:06:05,524
I think I should go home.

103
00:06:05,524 --> 00:06:07,957
I understand. I'm sorry about that.

104
00:06:07,957 --> 00:06:09,859
Do you want me to walk you home?

105
00:06:09,859 --> 00:06:12,951
It's all right. I can go by myself.

106
00:06:39,909 --> 00:06:42,030
I bet I'll get in a lot of trouble.

107
00:06:43,362 --> 00:06:46,535
Maybe it was better to leave my bag at Deok Hui's?

108
00:07:02,932 --> 00:07:04,353
Gosh...

109
00:07:05,434 --> 00:07:06,935
Ho Gu Hui.

110
00:07:08,098 --> 00:07:09,880
Did you use my computer again?

111
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:12,391
It's been slow all day for no reason.

112
00:07:12,391 --> 00:07:14,693
I didn't use it. Why would I?

113
00:07:14,693 --> 00:07:17,066
You didn't? In any case,

114
00:07:17,066 --> 00:07:19,859
if you ever touch my computer, I won't stand for it, all right?

115
00:07:19,859 --> 00:07:21,820
Are there things in there you don't want me to see?

116
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:24,954
Never. You must never see it.

117
00:07:24,954 --> 00:07:27,406
If it's embarrassing to show your little sister,

118
00:07:27,406 --> 00:07:30,359
you shouldn't be watching them either, Oppa.

119
00:07:30,359 --> 00:07:32,561
- Where's Mom and Dad? 
 - They're sleeping.

120
00:07:32,561 --> 00:07:35,113
You should go to bed, too.

121
00:07:45,594 --> 00:07:46,975
What?

122
00:07:47,846 --> 00:07:50,069
No one even knew?

123
00:07:55,184 --> 00:07:57,186
  That's how I ran away from home

124
00:07:57,186 --> 00:08:00,618
  and came back without anyone even knowing.

125
00:08:16,835 --> 00:08:18,157
What do you guys think?

126
00:08:18,157 --> 00:08:20,670
Can you see why people call French

127
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:22,160
the language of love?

128
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:25,534
For the next group assignment, get into pairs,

129
00:08:25,534 --> 00:08:28,558
find French signs on the street,

130
00:08:28,558 --> 00:08:31,020
and find out what they mean.

131
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:34,224
I'll know if you merely look them up on the Internet!

132
00:08:34,224 --> 00:08:37,457
If you're caught, you'll get a zero. Try if you think you can get away with it.

133
00:08:37,457 --> 00:08:40,779
So until next class...

134
00:08:40,779 --> 00:08:42,820
Au revoir. 
 (French: goodbye)

135
00:08:52,372 --> 00:08:54,394
Deok Hui, how about we...

136
00:08:54,394 --> 00:08:56,095
What's with the bag?

137
00:08:56,095 --> 00:08:58,748
I'm sorry. I have to leave early today.

138
00:08:58,748 --> 00:09:01,991
Mom wants me to go with her to see Samuel.

139
00:09:01,991 --> 00:09:04,493
I even have a note for an early leave.

140
00:09:04,493 --> 00:09:06,455
I'm off. Sorry.

141
00:09:06,455 --> 00:09:08,187
Bye.

142
00:09:17,566 --> 00:09:18,968
Why are you alone today?

143
00:09:18,968 --> 00:09:20,450
Where's Deok Hui?

144
00:09:20,450 --> 00:09:22,491
She went to a fan signing event.

145
00:09:22,491 --> 00:09:25,043
A fan signing event? For whom?

146
00:09:26,156 --> 00:09:27,636
Samuel?

147
00:09:27,636 --> 00:09:30,619
Her mom even signed an early leave slip so she could go.

148
00:09:30,619 --> 00:09:34,493
  This is Mo Nan Hui. She can fool even her own mother with her makeup skills.

149
00:09:34,493 --> 00:09:37,506
What kind of girl has brows like those?

150
00:09:37,506 --> 00:09:39,138
Come here.

151
00:09:49,007 --> 00:09:51,390
Did you know that my YouTube channel has over a million views?

152
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:53,372
Yes. Sure.

153
00:09:53,372 --> 00:09:56,775
Actually, I have a favor to ask you.

154
00:09:56,775 --> 00:09:58,007
What is it?

155
00:09:58,007 --> 00:09:59,939
I like Ji Hun.

156
00:10:01,730 --> 00:10:05,774
You're close to Ji Hun. Can you help me out?

157
00:10:05,774 --> 00:10:07,656
In return, I'll introduce you to someone.

158
00:10:07,656 --> 00:10:09,808
I know someone who'd be perfect for you.

159
00:10:09,808 --> 00:10:12,602
That's all right. You don't need to do that.

160
00:10:12,602 --> 00:10:15,254
Don't back out when you really want to.

161
00:10:17,496 --> 00:10:18,877
Come here.

162
00:10:23,132 --> 00:10:26,204
See? Don't you look much more vibrant?

163
00:10:28,046 --> 00:10:29,369
You can have this.

164
00:10:29,369 --> 00:10:31,049
What?

165
00:10:31,049 --> 00:10:34,513
Well... Thanks.

166
00:10:34,513 --> 00:10:37,005
I'm off. I appreciate your help.

167
00:10:49,698 --> 00:10:53,031
Gu Hui, the guy I told you about wants to meet you today.

168
00:10:53,031 --> 00:10:55,824
What? I told you I'm not interested.

169
00:10:55,824 --> 00:10:58,627
No, I already set it up.

170
00:10:58,627 --> 00:11:00,069
But I said I didn't want to.

171
00:11:00,069 --> 00:11:02,372
Can't you just go and see him for a second?

172
00:11:02,372 --> 00:11:04,003
Please, Gu Hui? Just once.

173
00:11:04,003 --> 00:11:05,083
Please.

174
00:11:05,083 --> 00:11:07,196
It's just that...

175
00:11:07,196 --> 00:11:10,429
You'll go, right? You're going, okay?

176
00:11:10,429 --> 00:11:13,182
- Gu Hui, you're so nice. I'm off. 
 - What?

177
00:11:26,396 --> 00:11:29,948
I'll just say hello

178
00:11:29,948 --> 00:11:32,081
and leave right away.

179
00:11:36,455 --> 00:11:38,116
Gu Hui,

180
00:11:38,116 --> 00:11:39,368
come over here.

181
00:11:39,368 --> 00:11:41,661
It's been so long.

182
00:11:41,661 --> 00:11:43,912
You've gotten prettier.

183
00:11:43,912 --> 00:11:45,634
What are you doing? Get over here.

184
00:11:45,634 --> 00:11:47,266
Come here.

185
00:11:47,266 --> 00:11:50,308
It's so nice to see you.

186
00:11:50,308 --> 00:11:53,652
We must be fated.

187
00:11:53,652 --> 00:11:55,425
I thought you had a girlfriend.

188
00:11:55,425 --> 00:11:56,676
We broke up.

189
00:11:56,676 --> 00:11:59,177
A nice girl like you is the best kind of girlfriend to have.

190
00:11:59,177 --> 00:12:00,580
I'm hungry.

191
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:03,482
I'll have the Beijing Spicy Chicken Burger set

192
00:12:03,482 --> 00:12:05,593
and Coke with a lot of ice.

193
00:12:16,446 --> 00:12:17,866
Revenge Note?

194
00:12:17,866 --> 00:12:22,590
I've had such bad luck ever since I got it. It drove me insane.

195
00:12:25,123 --> 00:12:26,895
Are you wearing makeup?

196
00:12:28,046 --> 00:12:30,469
You look a lot better. Keep it up.

197
00:12:30,469 --> 00:12:32,310
Eat up.

198
00:12:43,021 --> 00:12:44,393
You should come.

199
00:12:44,393 --> 00:12:46,565
Oh, my. Are you going to the hagwon?

200
00:12:46,565 --> 00:12:49,228
It's so good to run into you. Ji Hun, have you eaten?

201
00:12:49,228 --> 00:12:52,591
You haven't, right? Do you want to eat together? It'll be my treat.

202
00:12:52,591 --> 00:12:54,723
I'll have a hamburger.

203
00:12:54,723 --> 00:12:58,376
Let's go. It's free food.

204
00:12:59,619 --> 00:13:01,540
Just go.

205
00:13:01,540 --> 00:13:04,282
You know how hard it is to get free stuff?

206
00:13:09,167 --> 00:13:12,331
Gu Hui, I've caught you red-handed.

207
00:13:16,756 --> 00:13:19,057
Isn't he...

208
00:13:19,057 --> 00:13:21,119
- You know him? 
 - What?

209
00:13:23,312 --> 00:13:24,913
Well...

210
00:13:28,226 --> 00:13:31,451
We saw the two of you break up

211
00:13:31,451 --> 00:13:32,821
in front of the building.

212
00:13:32,821 --> 00:13:36,306
What do you mean, we broke up? We were just having a fight.

213
00:13:36,306 --> 00:13:40,278
I'm her first love. Isn't that right?

214
00:13:44,953 --> 00:13:46,686
Ji Hun, it's not...

215
00:13:46,686 --> 00:13:48,987
You two look great together.

216
00:13:48,987 --> 00:13:52,109
Ji Hun, should we go eat somewhere else?

217
00:13:57,296 --> 00:13:59,437
What about our hamburgers?

218
00:14:00,930 --> 00:14:04,454
What should we do this Saturday? I have some free time.

219
00:14:04,454 --> 00:14:06,014
You should bring some chicken.

220
00:14:06,014 --> 00:14:08,357
I remember your mom used to like me.

221
00:14:08,357 --> 00:14:12,009
You're not going to eat this? I'll eat it then.

222
00:14:15,864 --> 00:14:17,776
I'm sorry, but I think I should go.

223
00:14:17,776 --> 00:14:19,748
You should stay and eat.

224
00:14:38,337 --> 00:14:39,839
  Nan Hui: How's it going?

225
00:14:39,839 --> 00:14:41,139
  Jung Wu: Gu Hui is under control

226
00:14:41,139 --> 00:14:42,431
  You need to make it work on your end

227
00:14:42,431 --> 00:14:44,433
  He didn't seem interested in you though.

228
00:14:44,433 --> 00:14:47,766
  Nan Hui: None of your business.

229
00:14:51,481 --> 00:14:53,551
It was a misunderstanding...

230
00:14:54,734 --> 00:14:56,674
That won't do.

231
00:14:57,816 --> 00:15:00,158
He probably doesn't even care.

232
00:15:00,158 --> 00:15:03,332
Am I just overreacting?

233
00:15:03,332 --> 00:15:04,794
Gosh.

234
00:15:04,794 --> 00:15:07,124
What should I text him?

235
00:15:08,748 --> 00:15:10,269
Okay.

236
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,111
First loves are

237
00:15:13,111 --> 00:15:16,945
meant to be broken...

238
00:15:16,945 --> 00:15:20,489
Are you insane? Don't talk about your first love.

239
00:15:20,489 --> 00:15:23,872
That's not it. Should I text him or not?

240
00:15:23,872 --> 00:15:26,103
What should I write?

241
00:15:28,346 --> 00:15:31,949
They're shutting off the water soon. If you want to take a shower, do it now.

242
00:15:33,311 --> 00:15:35,024
Okay.

243
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:44,153
  God Ji Hun

244
00:15:49,748 --> 00:15:51,469
  God Ji Hun?

245
00:16:02,971 --> 00:16:04,572
Hello?

246
00:16:12,851 --> 00:16:16,324
Here. I answered a call for you.

247
00:16:25,403 --> 00:16:27,656
  Your call is being forwarded to voice mail.

248
00:16:27,656 --> 00:16:31,440
  Additional fee will be charged after the beep.

249
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:34,723
My gosh. Why did you answer my phone?

250
00:16:34,723 --> 00:16:35,855
What did you say?

251
00:16:35,855 --> 00:16:36,956
What did I say?

252
00:16:36,956 --> 00:16:38,087
  Hello?

253
00:16:38,087 --> 00:16:39,509
  Ten minutes ago

254
00:16:39,509 --> 00:16:41,079
  Isn't this Gu Hui's phone?

255
00:16:41,079 --> 00:16:42,951
  It is.

256
00:16:42,951 --> 00:16:45,183
  She's taking a shower right now.

257
00:16:45,183 --> 00:16:46,785
  Who is this?

258
00:16:46,785 --> 00:16:48,386
  Me?

259
00:16:48,386 --> 00:16:50,428
  I'm the one who showered first.

260
00:16:50,428 --> 00:16:52,280
  Where are you?

261
00:16:53,522 --> 00:16:56,125
  I'm on top of a bed.

262
00:16:56,125 --> 00:16:58,436
Are you insane?

263
00:16:58,436 --> 00:17:01,288
- Why, you crazy... 
 - Hey.

264
00:17:01,288 --> 00:17:03,001
You're crazy!

265
00:17:03,001 --> 00:17:05,194
How could you lie like that

